[h1]Function Parameters[/h1]

You can define a single function, and pass different parameter values (arguments) to it.[code format="js" codeId="678"]function sayHello(name) {
   alert("Hi, " + name);
}
sayHello("[b]David[/b]");
sayHello("[b]Sarah[/b]");
sayHello("[b]John[/b]");[/code]
[note]This will execute the function's code each time for the provided argument.[/note]
